arate are brought together in this book, which seeks to replicate the links between different areas of thought and action as they exist in reality and shape events.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 08. Jul 2019) 0aAuerstedt, Battle of, Auerstedt, Germany, 1806. 0aJena, Battle of, Jena, Germany, 1806. 0aMilitary art and sciencevCase studies. 0aMilitary historyvCase studies. 0aNapoleonic Wars, 1800-1815vArt and the wars. 0aNapoleonic Wars, 1800-1815xCampaignszGermanyzPrussia. 0aNapoleonic Wars, 1800-1815xLiterature and the wars. 0aNapoleonic Wars, 1800-1815xSocial aspectszGermanyzPrussia. 7aHISTORY / Military / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPUP eBook-Package 2000-2015z978311066258008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPrinceton eBook Package Backlist 2000-2013z978311044250208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPrinceton eBook Package Backlist 2000-2014z978311045953140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781400831340zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781400831340.jpg  a978-3-11-044250-2  Princeton eBook Package Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  a978-3-11-045953-1  Princeton eBook Package Backlist 2000-2014c2000d2014  a978-3-11-066258-0  PUP eBook-Package 2000-2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aPDA7ENG  aPDA9PRIN